## Quick Start

```bash
# 1. Copy and fill in environment variables
cp .env.example .env

# 2. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
# or (recommended)
uv sync

# 3. Run the application
uvicorn src.main:app --reload
```

API docs: http://localhost:8000/docs

